summary: This document is a Facebook business record produced in response to a legal request, detailing account information for a specific user. It shows the account was created in 2013, was active through 2019, and includes login timestamps and a verified phone number. No NCMEC cybertip reports or financial payment details were found for the specified date range.

keyFacts: The Facebook account was created on February 9, 2013, and was still active as of the record generation in late 2019.
A cell phone number associated with the account was verified on February 12, 2016.
The record shows multiple login events to the account between April and July 2019, but no specific location data is provided.
No NCMEC (National Center for Missing & Exploited Children) cybertip reports were associated with this account for the date range January 1, 2019, to November 21, 2019.
No responsive records were found for registered credit cards, PayPal accounts, or direct debit information linked to the account.
